<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/html">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <span class="searchLabel">
        <label for="alfa">freetext search v. </label>
        <img src="/pic/a.gif" id="alfa" alt="alfa" width="20" height="20" />
    </span>
    <span class="input-group" style="display: inline-table;">
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="search"
               placeholder="audi a4 allroad von 18.000 bis 20.000 € ab 2010 in Erding"
               spellcheck="false" autocomplete="off">
          <span class="input-group-btn">
            <button  id="btnsearch" class="btn btn-default" type="button">Search</button>
          </span>
    </span>

    <div id="suggestions" class="shadowed-flying-box"></div>
    <div id="glaskugel"></div>
    <div id="nixverstehen"></div>

    <button style="margin-top: 50px" type="button" class="btn btn-success" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseExample" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">
        Help
    </button>
    <div class="collapse" id="collapseExample">
      <div class="well">
        <h4>a couple of thoughts</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>please consider this solution as an extension and not as replacement of the current search implementation.</li>
            <li>right now its just a mapping for existing filter, e.g. terms like "mp3 player" are not found cause we don't have this information in Elasticsearch</li>
            <li>cluster terms are possible, right now "sportwagen" and "familienwagen", if you have ideas for further clustering, just give feedback.</li>
            <li>the autocompletion is weird because its used directly from google and gives back thing which have nothing to do with cars. Better would be the usage of an own autocompletion (based for example on Elasticsearch).</li>
        </ul>
        <h4>possible examples</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>audi a4 allroad ab 2009 für 18.000 20.000 € in Erding</li>
            <li>bmw 1er benziner in München 20 km jahreswagen</li>
            <li>Polo alle</li>
            <li>Mercedes gebraucht oder neu diesel 4 - 6 türen </li>
            <li>BMW motorrad 85435 in gelb metalic 180 - 220 ps</li>
            <li>audi cabrio oder kleinwagen automatik 150 KW</li>
            <li>VW Touran 20000 €  2 7 Sitze händler erstzulassung 2012</li>
            <li>Benz mit cd Klima servo und bordcomputer</li>
            <li>audi Schaltgetriebe Zulassung von 2009 bis 2014</li>
            <li>Ford Focus 6500 km online seit vorgestern mit bildern</li>
            <li>VW Golf Plus mit video 4 Hand</li>
            <li>bmw von 2 bis 3 Halter eingestelt seit 1 Woche</li>
            <li>Audi blub unfallfahrzeug oder wrack</li>
            <li>Special Muri variante mercedes cl 500</li>
            <li>merc cl500</li>
            <li>cool, dass du bis hierher gelesen hast :-)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="http://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/bundle.js"></script>
</body>
</html>